author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
"The End" is taken from Wolfgang Van Halen's upcoming album with his band Mammoth - formerly Mammoth WVH, now just Mammoth.  Accompanying the single is an epic video. Everyone is in it - except Corey Feldman. 

To watch the whole thing uninterrupted: https://youtu.be/7w7rAEnMXDI?si=3rDxdnbpkDtG1du3

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The new Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is available now: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory
